{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"SVG image element","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_Image_Tag","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_fonts\">« zurück</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Tools_for_SVG\">weiter  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>\n\n<p>Das SVG <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-Element erlaubt es, Rasterbilder innerhalb von SVG-Objekten einzufügen.</p>\n\n<p>In diesem Beispiel wird ein .jpg-Bild, aufgerufen durch das <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/xlink:href\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">xlink:href (en-US)</a></code>-Attribut, in ein SVG-Objekt eingefügt:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token prolog\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" standalone=\"no\"?&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">svg</span> <span class=\"token name\">PUBLIC</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-//W3C//DTD SVG 1.1//EN\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/1.1/DTD/svg11.dtd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5cm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>4cm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>xlink</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>image</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xlink:</span>href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>firefox.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Folgende wichtige Punkte müsse beachtet werden (festgelegt in den <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#ImageElement\" rel=\" noopener\">W3-Spezifikationen</a>):</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>\n  <p>Wurde kein Attribut x (oder y) angegeben, wird dafür automatisch 0 gesetzt.</p>\n </li>\n <li>\n  <p>Wurde kein Attribut height (oder width) angegeben, wird dafür automatisch 0 gesetzt.</p>\n </li>\n <li>Ist das Attribut height (oder width) 0, wird das Rendern des Bildes deaktiviert.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_fonts\">« zurück</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Tools_for_SVG\">weiter  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Das SVG <image> (en-US)-Element erlaubt es, Rasterbilder innerhalb von SVG-Objekten einzufügen.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SVG image element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SVG: Elément image","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SVG の image 要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"SVG 이미지 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"SVG image element","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"SVG image element","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/svg/tutorial/svg_image_tag","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/svg/tutorial/svg_image_tag/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial","title":"Tutorial"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_Image_Tag","title":"SVG image element"}],"pageTitle":"SVG image element - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}